    <string-array name="quickspace_psa_morning">
        <item>Good morning. Welcome to the Matrixx.</item>
        <item>Boot up your day — smooth, fast, unstoppable.</item>
        <item>Another day, another level of customization.</item>
        <item>Start clean. Stay smooth. Stay Matrixx.</item>
        <item>Power meets perfection. Let’s begin.</item>
        <item>Your system is stable. Your day should be too.</item>
        <item>Wake up to speed, stability, and style.</item>
        <item>Fresh start. Zero lag. Full control.</item>
        <item>Performance ready. Are you?</item>
        <item>Every sunrise deserves a smooth experience.</item>
        <item>Today runs on Matrixx.</item>
        <item>Optimized for greatness. Just like you.</item>
    </string-array>
    <string-array name="quickspace_psa_noon">
        <item>Still smooth? That’s Matrixx.</item>
        <item>No lags. No limits. Just performance.</item>
        <item>Midday check: Everything running flawless.</item>
        <item>Keep pushing — your ROM already is.</item>
        <item>Customization at its peak. Stay in control.</item>
        <item>Performance that lasts all day.</item>
        <item>Speed you can feel. Stability you can trust.</item>
        <item>No compromises. Just Matrixx.</item>
        <item>Your device. Your rules.</item>
        <item>Power through — you’re optimized.</item>
    </string-array>
    <string-array name="quickspace_psa_early_evening">
        <item>Still running smooth. Just like expected.</item>
        <item>Evening vibes, zero stutters.</item>
        <item>Performance doesn’t clock out.</item>
        <item>Relax — Matrixx handles the rest.</item>
        <item>From morning to now — still flawless.</item>
        <item>Consistency is power.</item>
        <item>Stay fluid. Stay fast.</item>
        <item>Built for endurance. Built for you.</item>
    </string-array>
    <string-array name="quickspace_psa_evening">
        <item>Smooth nights start with Matrixx.</item>
        <item>No drops. No drama. Just perfection.</item>
        <item>Wind down, your system already did the work.</item>
        <item>Performance never sleeps.</item>
        <item>Dark mode. Smooth mode. Matrixx mode.</item>
        <item>End the day on a stable note.</item>
        <item>Flawless till the last tap.</item>
    </string-array>
    <string-array name="quickspace_psa_midnight">
        <item>Late night. Full control.</item>
        <item>While others sleep, Matrixx performs.</item>
        <item>Optimized for night owls.</item>
        <item>Silence outside. Power inside.</item>
        <item>No limits. No slowdowns.</item>
        <item>Midnight sessions, maximum smoothness.</item>
        <item>Stable. Silent. Strong.</item>
    </string-array>
    <string-array name="quickspace_psa_random">
        <item>Welcome to Matrixx.</item>
        <item>Built different. Runs better.</item>
        <item>Flash once. Stay forever.</item>
        <item>Lag is not in our vocabulary.</item>
        <item>Customize everything. Regret nothing.</item>
        <item>Powered by stability.</item>
        <item>More features. Less nonsense.</item>
        <item>This is what smooth feels like.</item>
        <item>Not stock. Not basic. Matrixx.</item>
        <item>Your device just leveled up.</item>
        <item>Engineered for perfection.</item>
        <item>Clean. Fast. Reliable.</item>
        <item>Experience the difference.</item>
        <item>Zero compromises.</item>
        <item>Performance unlocked.</item>
        <item>Stay smooth. Stay Matrixx.</item>
        <item>Crafted for power users.</item>
        <item>Control every pixel.</item>
        <item>More control than ever.</item>
        <item>Because stock is boring.</item>
    </string-array>
